      <title>麦格理称印尼减产可能导致全球镍供应量减少 35%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/indonesia-nickel-move-may-cut-global-supply-35-macquarie-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦格理集团有限公司 (Macquarie Group Ltd.) 表示，印尼镍矿产量可能下降，导致全球镍市场供应减少三分之一以上，给镍价带来巨大的上行风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/indonesia-nickel-move-may-cut-global-supply-35-macquarie-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 04:25:05 GMT</pubDate>
